# mkfs.ntfs

> Creates a NTFS filesystem inside a partition
> More information: https://manned.org/mkfs.ntfs

- Create a NTFS filesystem inside partition 1 on device b (`sdb1`):

`mkfs.ntfs {string value: /dev/sdb1}`

- Create filesystem with a volume-label:

`mkfs.ntfs -L {string value: volume_label} {string value: /dev/sdb1}`

- Create filesystem with specific UUID:

`mkfs.ntfs -U {string value: UUID} {string value: /dev/sdb1}`
